                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "A creature that slays a draugr is subjected to a <a aonid=\"184\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>mariner's curse</i></a> spell with a save DC of 17. The curse ends if the draugr is buried in a calm sea or after 1 week passes."
